-- Belka Sees Polish Inflation `Under Control' on Fragile Economic Recovery
-- David McQuaid
-- 2010-06-18T04:53:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-18/belka-sees-polish-inflation-under-control-on-fragile-economic-recovery.html

          
          
             Polish inflation is under control
thanks to a “relatively fragile” recovery and a high
unemployment rate, which is keeping economic growth below
potential, central bank Governor Marek Belka said in an
interview published today in Gazeta Wyborcza.  
          
          


  


        